P_HTM[3793]="*anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**imprudent …*";
P_HTM[3794]="*asamāhitā asamāhitehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**lacking immersion …*";
P_HTM[3795]="*duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti.**witless …*";
P_HTM[3796]="*Saddhā saddhehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**The faithful with the faithful …*";
P_HTM[3797]="*hirimanā hirimanehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**conscientious …*";
P_HTM[3798]="*ottappino ottappīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**prudent...*";
P_HTM[3799]="*samāhitā samāhitehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**possessing immersion …*";
P_HTM[3800]="*paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samentī”ti.**and the wise with the wise.”*";
P_HTM[3801]="*Paṭhamaṃ.* **";
