P_HTM[3816]="*3. Pañcasikkhāpadasuttaṃ**The Five Precepts*";
P_HTM[3817]="*Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati.**At Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[3818]="*“Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṃsandanti samenti.**“Mendicants, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element:*";
P_HTM[3819]="*Pāṇātipātino pāṇātipātīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**those who kill living creatures with those who kill living creatures,*";
P_HTM[3820]="*adinnādāyino adinnādāyīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**those who steal …*";
P_HTM[3821]="*kāmesumicchācārino kāmesumicchācārīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**commit sexual misconduct …*";
P_HTM[3822]="*musāvādino musāvādīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**lie …*";
P_HTM[3823]="*surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhāyino surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhāyīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti.**consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence …*";
P_HTM[3824]="*Pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā pāṇātipātā paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**Those who refrain from killing living creatures …*";
P_HTM[3825]="*adinnādānā paṭiviratā adinnādānā paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**who refrain from stealing …*";
P_HTM[3826]="*kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratā kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**who refrain from sexual misconduct …*";
P_HTM[3827]="*musāvādā paṭiviratā musāvādā paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**who refrain from lying …*";
P_HTM[3828]="*surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratā surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samentī”ti.**those who refrain from consuming alcoholic drinks that cause negligence with those who refrain from consuming alcoholic drinks that cause negligence.”*";
P_HTM[3829]="*Tatiyaṃ.* **";
P_HTM[3830]="*4. Sattakammapathasuttaṃ**Seven Ways of Performing Deeds*";
