P_HTM[3833]="*Pāṇātipātino pāṇātipātīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**those who kill living creatures with those who kill living creatures,*";
P_HTM[3834]="*adinnādāyino adinnādāyīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**those who steal …*";
