P_HTM[3840]="*Pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā … pe …**Those who refrain from killing living creatures. …*";
P_HTM[3841]="*adinnādānā paṭiviratā …**who refrain from stealing …*";
P_HTM[3842]="*kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratā …**who refrain from sexual misconduct …*";
P_HTM[3843]="*musāvādā paṭiviratā …**who refrain from lying …*";
P_HTM[3844]="*pisuṇāya vācāya paṭiviratā pisuṇāya vācāya paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**who refrain from divisive speech …*";
P_HTM[3845]="*pharusāya vācāya paṭiviratā pharusāya vācāya paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;**who refrain from harsh speech …*";
P_HTM[3846]="*samphappalāpā paṭiviratā samphappalāpā paṭiviratehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samentī”ti.**who refrain from talking nonsense with those who refrain from talking nonsense.”*";
P_HTM[3847]="*Catutthaṃ.* **";
